    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\n`--api-info`/api metadata has lost all `ArrayOf` types.\n\nBisected the issue to https://github.com/neovim/neovim/commit/76de3e2d07f20c77b7ee6f72c8ec27b045e51ed1\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n`nvim --api-info | strings | grep -i arrayof`\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nPrevious `ArrayOf` etc. types are present.\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.12.0\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nPopos\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nAny\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nAny\n\n### Installation\n\nbuild from repo",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
