        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "It's unstable in the sense that emmylua annotations are unstable; it unblocks consumers for the purpose of a build step; and it leaves the door open for a \"stable\" solution later.\n\nAlso, it could be \"stable\" if we decide to provide reified data-structures similar to `eval.lua` (i.e. [item 2](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/38734#issuecomment-4188997882)).",
